will even work?

155
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,041
We have no choice.

156
00:13:37,875 --> 00:13:39,875
We've got to start somewhere, sometime.

157
00:13:40,666 --> 00:13:42,250
Because today they've
only crossed our threshold,

158
00:13:42,791 --> 00:13:44,000
